<item>
            <title>[SOLR-7392] SOLR_JAVA_MEM setting in solr.in.sh ignored</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7392</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In Solr 5.1 the following line was added to bin/solr line 1262:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;SOLR_JAVA_MEM=()&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This overrides any setting previously read from solr.in.sh. Only SOLR_HEAP setting could have effect, but it&apos;s not even mentioned in solr.in.sh.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
